---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Support the Cause — Mu Alpha Theta" description="Coaching is free. Families who wish to give can support underprivileged children in India — 100% of contributions go toward daily necessities of life.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow">Support the Cause</p>
      <h1 style="max-width: 22ch;">Learning math here. Changing lives an ocean away.</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Our coaching is, and always will be, free. But the deeper purpose of this initiative is
        to use mathematics as a means of serving others. Families who wish to give are warmly
        invited — never required — to help underprivileged children in India meet the daily
        necessities of life.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap grid grid--2">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Where it goes</p>
        <h2>Daily necessities, for children who need them most.</h2>
        <p>
          Contributions are directed toward food, clothing, school supplies, and the everyday
          essentials that many children in India go without. Our goal is to donate on an
          international scale — to let the discipline and excellence we build here ripple
          outward into real help for those who need it.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>An honest note</h3>
        <p>
          We are a <strong>student-led initiative</strong>, not a registered nonprofit, so
          contributions are <strong>not tax-deductible</strong>. Every dollar given is directed
          to the cause — no overhead, no salaries.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-0">
          We believe in complete transparency about how funds are raised and used.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap callout">
      <p class="eyebrow" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);">How to give</p>
      <h2>Want to contribute?</h2>
      <p class="lead">
        We're setting up a simple, secure way to accept optional donations. In the meantime, if
        you'd like to give or learn more about the cause, please reach out — we'd love to tell
        you exactly where your support goes.
      </p>
      <div style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
        <a class="btn btn--primary" href="mailto:mualphatheta@gmail.com?subject=Supporting%20the%20cause">Email us to give</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
